lead_paragraph: Former world 100 meters champion Tyson Gay has traded the track for ice this week after he entered to compete in the U.S. Bobsled National Push Championships in Calgary.

headline.print_headline: Gay Looks to Set Pace on Ice at Bobsled Championships
